snippet.title: As The Fog Burns - A Connor Sherlock "Walking Simulator"
snippet.description:
I've got to stop walking to the edge of game worlds.

This is the fifth of Connor Sherlock's monthly releases, following Birthplace of Ossian and Irrelevance V. They're weirdly engrossing, atmospheric, and are pretty terrible for YouTube audiences, so I'm really looking forward to them!

You can get this and future works of Connor Sherlock at his Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/connorsherlock

• SUBSCRIBE: http://goo.gl/E3y5FX
Patreon: http://patreon.com/kurtjmac
Twitter: http://twitter.com/kurtjmac
Livestream: http://twitch.tv/kurtjmac

Thanks for watching! Like, favorite, subscribe, whatnot, indeed, and etcetera!
